'''Sarah Magaajyia Silberfel'''d (yavutse 30 Kanama 1996) ni umukinnyi n'umuyobozi wa filimi muri [[Nijeriya]] ariko akomoka mu [[Bufaransa]]

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Silberfeld ni umukobwa w'umuyobozi wa firime Rahmatou Keïta n'umunyamakuru w’umufaransa Antoine Silber . <ref name=":1">https://www.letemps.ch/culture/fardeau-couleur-peau-0</ref> Yatangiye gukina kuri theatre yaho afite imyaka 11. Silberfeld yakuriye mu Bufaransa ariko agenda kenshi mu Bugereki, Nigeriya, na Mali, aba i Los Angeles imyaka itatu. <ref name=":0">https://fr.petitsfrenchies.com/interview-de-magaajyia-silberfeld-realisatrice-et-actrice/</ref> Yatangiye gukina filime muri 2011, i ''La Lisière'' . <ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=50886</ref> Silberfeld yize ibijyanye no gukina mu kigo cya Lee Strasberg mu 2013, muri Playhouse West Repertory Theatre muri 2014 ndetse no muri Studio ya Susan Batson mu 2015. <ref>http://www.filmtalents.com/fiche.cfm/115_1-628549-magaajyia_silberfeld.html</ref> <ref>https://www.rts.ch/info/culture/cinema/10298663-le-fiff-offre-une-carte-blanche-a-16-actrices-noires-et-metisses.html</ref> Afite imyaka 18, yanditse kandi ayobora film ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Me Hano'' kandi afatanya kuyobora ''Ride cyangwa Die'' irimo Piper de Palma na Roxane Depardieu. <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/magaajyia-silberfeld/</ref>

Muri 2016, Silberfeld yagize uruhare rwe rwa mbere muri ''The Wedding Ring'', iyobowe na nyina kandi yatewe inkunga yose binyuze mumafaranga ya Afrika. Yakinnye na Tiyaa, umukobwa ukiri muto ujya kwiga mubufaransa agakundana numugabo ukomoka mubyubahiro.  Filime ibaye film ya mbere ya Nigeriya yakinnye muri Awards Awards. <ref>https://www.lepoint.fr/culture/cinema-oscars-2019-zin-naariya-de-rahmatou-keita-dans-la-course-03-12-2018-2276300_3.php</ref> Muri 2017, yayoboye filime ye ngufi ''Vagabonds'', yakinnye na Danny Glover . <ref name=":0" /> Muri uwo mwaka, Silberfeld yabonye impamyabumenyi ya filozofiya na Sorbonne . <ref name="karolle">https://www.globetrottermag.com/news-features/2017/4/3/magaajyia-silberfeld</ref> Mugihe cya kaminuza, yize icyongereza abinyujije muri firime zo muri [[Amerika]]. <ref name=":0" />

Yabaye umuyobozi mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime ya Friborg 2019 kandi atera inkunga Amasezerano y’uburinganire n'ubwuzuzanye. <ref>https://www.fiff.ch/fr/le-fiff-sengage-pour-la-parite</ref> Silberfeld yerekanye documentaire ya nyina ''Al'lèèssi.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Une actrice africaine'' (2004), ifoto yumukinnyi wa Nigeriya Zalika Souley  . 

